            <title>[JDK-8299844] RISC-V: Implement _onSpinWait intrinsic</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8299844</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>Implement _onSpinWait() intrinsic for RISC-V, and it can be implemented by using PAUSE instruction from Zihintpause Extension, which is ratified and a mandatory extension of RVA22U64 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/riscv/riscv-profiles/blob/main/profiles.adoc#rva22u64-mandatory-extensions&quot;&gt;https://github.com/riscv/riscv-profiles/blob/main/profiles.adoc#rva22u64-mandatory-extensions&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;br/&gt;
Software can use the PAUSE instruction to reduce energy consumption while executing spinwait&lt;br/&gt;
code sequences (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/riscv/riscv-isa-manual/blob/master/src/zihintpause.tex&quot;&gt;https://github.com/riscv/riscv-isa-manual/blob/master/src/zihintpause.tex&lt;/a&gt;).</description>
